    Gutclaw stepped in front of Headsh=
ot, rudely.

    "Us Bodicons haven't even been tickled since we landed on =
this rock," Gutclaw said.

      The other Bodicons just nodded.  Headshot =
sneered at Gutclaw.

      "Yeehaw!  Looks like we get to do the fun stuff!=
" Legtrap said in pleasure.

     Meanwhile, Decapitron went to where Megat=
ron was.  He saw the other Bodicons, but then looked back to Megatron.

   =
  "I'm here Megatron.  So explain my job," Decapitron said.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~=

     Skullgrin stood silent, ready for guard d=
uty.

     "I can't wait till I do something exciting...." Skullgrin said q=
uietly to himself in a cold voice.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~=

     Triggerhappy looked at Megatron.

     "Yes, sir!" Triggerhappy sa=
id as he was given orders, then he looked at FireBlade and the Bodicons, an=
d Autofire.

     "So guys, we get a mission!  Doesn't that sound fun?" Tri=
ggerhappy said.
